#. Tag: para
#: credits-and-licenses.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are the people who deserve the most credit for initially creating "
"&kmail; and raising it from its birth in 1997 through its early childhood "
"<emphasis>ca.</emphasis> 2005. They may be regarded as the parents of "
"&kmail;. A handful of them are still contributing code and bug fixes to the "
"project today."
msgstr ""
"To so ljudje, ki si zaslužijo največ zaslug za začetno ustvarjanje &kmail;-a "
"in so ga vzgajali od njegovega rojstva leta 1997 do zgodnjega otroštva "
"<emphasis> ca.</emphasis> 2005. Lahko se štejejo za starše &kmail;-a. "
"Peščica izmed njih še danes prispeva kodo in popravke napak k projektu."

